d['en']['casestudies.cs2_title']='PT Manufacturing Corp Restructuring';
d['en']['casestudies.cs2_value']='Valuation: USD 35 Million';
d['en']['casestudies.cs2_p1']='Chatura guided the operational restructuring and capital optimization for a leading Indonesian manufacturer, enabling the company to increase production capacity by 40% without compromising financial health.';
d['en']['casestudies.cs2_p2']='This engagement covered long-term liability reshuffling and comprehensive corporate income tax compliance audits following the implementation of new tax legislation, securing the operational cash flow of an entity in the Cikarang industrial estate.';
d['en']['casestudies.cs2_p3']='Through in-depth analysis of structural overhead inefficiencies, our team successfully redesigned the liquidity architecture, yielding significant operational cost savings for the local manufacturing conglomerate.';
d['en']['casestudies.cs3_tag']='Technology';
d['en']['casestudies.cs3_title']='Series C Funding Advisory FinTech Unicorn';
d['en']['casestudies.cs3_value']='Valuation: USD 80 Million';
d['en']['casestudies.cs3_p1']='Chatura served as financial advisor for a leading Indonesian fintech company in its Series C funding round, structuring the deal to optimize valuation while maintaining founder control and investor alignment.';
d['en']['casestudies.cs3_p2']='In this engagement, we focused on structuring the deal to optimize valuation while preserving founder control and investor alignment. This alignment provides long-term technology expansion flexibility for corporations in the ASEAN regional market.';
d['en']['casestudies.cs3_p3']='OJK compliance validation, digital asset escrow structures, and intangible asset valuation became critical components that we handled in parallel to ensure smooth cross-border transactions between Singapore regional entities and local Indonesian technology companies.';
d['en']['casestudies.cs4_tag']='Healthcare';
d['en']['casestudies.cs4_title']='Regional Hospital Group Consolidation';
d['en']['casestudies.cs4_value']='Valuation: USD 25 Million';
d['en']['casestudies.cs4_p1']='Chatura guided the consolidation of three regional hospital groups into an integrated healthcare network, optimizing the transaction structure for tax efficiency while ensuring regulatory compliance across all jurisdictions.';
d['en']['casestudies.cs4_p2']='Post-merger, consolidated financial statement integration and cross-entity accounting standard harmonization became primary challenges that required precise resolution. Our team guided the entire holding restructuring process to ensure operational cash flow stability.';
d['en']['casestudies.cs4_p3']='Universal health coverage compliance confirmation and healthcare tax incentive framework adjustments became key pillars guaranteeing the long-term operational sustainability of this integrated hospital network.';
