d['en']['casestudies.cs5_title']='FMCG Brand Portfolio Optimization';
d['en']['casestudies.cs5_value']='Valuation: USD 40 Million';
d['en']['casestudies.cs5_p1']='Chatura advised a leading consumer goods company on portfolio optimization through selective divestitures and strategic acquisitions, resulting in a 25% improvement in operational margins within 18 months.';
d['en']['casestudies.cs5_p2']='Our approach included in-depth analysis of cross-category SKU performance, identification of non-core assets with divestiture potential, and structuring premium brand acquisition deals aligned with the client\'s long-term growth vision.';
